Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/rock_slide">Rock Slide</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/rock_slide">Rock Slide</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>Large boulders are hurled at the foe to inflict damage. It may also make the target flinch.</p>